                    "[WheatNotGrazed].Wheat.AboveGround.Wt*10 as TotalBiomassUngrazed",
                    "[WheatNotGrazed].Wheat.Grain.Wt*10 as TotalYieldUngrazed",
                    "[WheatSheep].Wheat.Phenology.Zadok.Stage as Zadok"
